ent/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-washing-with-water-768x577.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-washing-with-water-250x188.jpg.webp 250w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-washing-with-water-500x375.jpg.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="https://www.shopmimigreen.com/personalized-beaded-friendship-bracelet-dog-collar/" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Check Price on Mimi Green</span></a></div>\n<h3>Nostalgic Style Made With High-End Materials</h3>\n<p>The friendship bracelets we used to make as kids aren’t quite pet-friendly (I remember them even pinching me in the wrist as a child!), but Mimi Green took this design and adapted it for your four-legged best friend.</p>\n<p>Each bead is made of BPA-free 15mm Soft Touch Silicone Beads, which won’t hurt your pup if they push against them. The silicone is also very comfortable for long-term wear. The buckle is contoured to flow with the round shape of your dog’s neck (rather than being flat). All three buckle options are also known as quick-release buckles, they are easy to pinch open. The buckles are attached to lightweight waterproof biothane tabs.</p>\n<p>The actual “string” that runs through the collar is 1/16 Stainless Steel Cable, which features a 368lbs breaking strength. This being said, I would not recommend using this collar on a dog that tugs a lot &#8211; not because it might break, but because the collar is beaded and may not be suitable for strong pullers.</p>\n<h3>Different Sizes Available</h3>\n<p>There are 17 sizes available for dogs ranging from small (11”) to extra-large (27”). If your pup is between sizes, Mimi Green can make custom sizes as well. Collar width is also customizable, with widths ranging from 5/8” wide, 3/4&#8243; wide, or 1” wide.</p>\n<h3>Fully Customizable</h3>\n<p>Most aspects of the Custom Beaded Dog Collar Friendship Bracelet Style are fully customizable.</p>\n<p>For starters, you can choose between one strand of beads or two. Next, you can personalize the text beads on your collar with either your pet’s name, a phrase, or a phone number (up to 12 characters).</p>\n<p>Your bead color options range from multicolor, white, yellow, pink, purple, teal, and raspberry. You then select from either a heart or a star shape bead, both of which come in either white, yellow, pink, purple, or teal.</p>\n<p>There are three quick-release buckle options: MG2 plastic, Satin Hybrid, or Brass Hybrid. These buckles can be custom engraved for an additional fee. Engraving options include up to three text/number lines and 12 different fonts. A D-ring is included, but additional D-rings can be added.</p>\n<p>Mimi Green also accepts special requests &#8211; you can contact the company prior to ordering and see if your request can be done.</p>\n<h3>Easily Cleaned</h3>\n<p>The Custom Beaded Dog Collar Friendship Bracelet Style is designed to be easy to clean, so your pup can be rambunctious outdoors without worry. Just rinse with water and a gentle soap (if needed) in the sink, and it’ll be good to go. Biothane and silicone don’t tend to stain or hold dirt. As you can imagine, all of the materials are waterproof (hence being able to be washed in the sink).</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcse