ng her with the Custom Beaded Dog Collar Friendship Bracelet Style was very easy. Cleaning the collar was also very simple, a quick rinse in the sink.</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-764435" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-dog-wearing-the-leash.jpg" alt="Custom Beaded Dog Collar Friendship Bracelet Style Review - dog wearing the leash" width="1500" height="1126" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-dog-wearing-the-leash.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-dog-wearing-the-leash-600x450.jpg.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-dog-wearing-the-leash-800x601.jpg.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-dog-wearing-the-leash-768x577.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-dog-wearing-the-leash-250x188.jpg.webp 250w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-dog-wearing-the-leash-500x375.jpg.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="https://www.shopmimigreen.com/personalized-beaded-friendship-bracelet-dog-collar/" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Check Price on Mimi Green</span></a></div>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>\n<h3>How Do I Measure My Dog?</h3>\n<p>Take a <a href="https://www.dogster.com/lifestyle/how-to-measure-a-dog-for-a-collar" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="internal">tape measure and wrap it around the middle of your dog’s neck</a> (where the collar would best sit). Make sure your pup is standing when measuring, because the measurement could be a bit different when your dog sits!</p>\n<p>A big note is <em>not</em> to measure your dog’s existing flat-buckle collars &#8211; because this collar is beaded, the size will not align. Beaded collars are measured by circumference, while flat collars are measured by length.</p>\n<p>If this collar is intended to be used for walking (not just a fashionable accessory), be sure that the size is snug-enough to not slide off when walking on a leash.</p>\n<h3>What If My Dog Is a Leash-Tugger?</h3>\n<p>This collar is not meant for dogs that tend to be rambunctious on walks &#8211; this is a beaded collar, not a flat collar. I feel it would pinch, and the bead shapes would dig in and be<a href="https://www.dogster.com/dog-training/how-to-stop-a-dog-from-pulling-while-walking" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="internal"> uncomfortable for dogs that pull</a> on their collars a lot.</p>\n<h3>What If I Want Further Customizations Beyond the Ordering Page?</h3>\n<p>You can feel welcome to contact <a href="https://www.shopmimigreen.com/contact-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">Mimi Green</a> for custom requests! They do their best to accommodate.</p>\n<h3>What If the Collar Doesn’t Fit My Dog?</h3>\n<p>If you ordered the wrong size, reach out to Mimi Green within 7 days and they will send you a one-time code for free shipping and a 50% off coupon to order the correct size! This also applies if you typed in your engraving wrong, or if your dog damaged the collar within the first year.</p>\n<h3>Is It Possible To Use the Collar On a Cat?</h3>\n<p>Size-wise it may be possible, but the collar is really designed for use on a dog. Cats do best with breakaway collars because of how they climb around, and this is not a breakaway!</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-764433" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-product-on-harness.jpg" alt="Custom Beaded Dog Collar Friendship Bracelet Style Review - product on harness" width="1500" height="1126" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-product-on-harness.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-product-on-harness-600x450.jpg.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Custom-Beaded-Dog-Collar-Friendship-Bracelet-Style-Review-product-on-harness-800x601.jpg.webp 80