0/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>Is the Summer Mesh Harness a Good Value?</h2>\n<p>This harness is a great value. Along with being durable and high-quality, it does a great job of keeping your dog secure on walks and cool in warm weather. The EZ grip handle is perfect for when you need to get ahold of your pup and the reflective strap keeps your dog safe when the sun goes down. Overall, I’d say this harness is a solid choice and a great value for the money.</p>\n<h3>How We Tested</h3>\n<p>I initially put the harness on Micah to see if it fit. Micah is a 54 lb Standard Goldendoodle and measures 28” around his chest. According to his measurements, he’s borderline between a medium and a large. I ended up going with a large based on his weight and it’s a perfect fit! The straps are adjusted almost as large as they’ll go, giving him a little bit of wiggle room without being too tight.</p>\n<p>Once the harness was on Micah, I took him outside for a test run. I walked him around my driveway for a little while before taking him on a walk around my neighborhood. Both walks went great and I’ve continued to use the harness on every walk since!</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-764043" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-walking-dog-with-harness.jpg" alt="Joyride Summer Mesh Harness Review - walking dog with harness" width="1500" height="1215" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-walking-dog-with-harness.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-walking-dog-with-harness-600x486.jpg.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-walking-dog-with-harness-800x648.jpg.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-walking-dog-with-harness-768x622.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-walking-dog-with-harness-250x203.jpg.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="http://shrsl.com/4vfwu" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Check Latest Price</span></a></div>\n<h2><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></h2>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>\n<h3>Are the nametags included?</h3>\n<p>Yes! Joyride includes 13 free interchangeable and customizable nametags with each harness. There are a few pre-made options like, “Emotional Support” and <a href="https://www.dogster.com/lifestyle/national-hug-your-dog-day" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="internal">“Free Hugs”</a>, as well as a few blank tags for you to write your pup’s name or create your own.</p>\n<h3>Are there other styles and patterns?</h3>\n<p>Joyride makes a variety of harnesses in different styles and patterns. They have everything from a NightSafe light-up harness to a 2 in 1 jacket harness. They also have a pattern for every season.</p>\n<div class="su-box su-box-style-default" id="" style="border-color:#004288;border-radius:0px"><div class="su-box-title" style="background-color:#2575BB;color:#FFFFFF;border-top-left-radius:0px;border-top-right-radius:0px">A few of their patterns include:</div><div class="su-box-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim" style="border-bottom-left-radius:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px"><div class="su-list" style="margin-left:0px">\n<ul>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Flowers</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Plaid</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Snowflakes</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Camo</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Skulls</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Hearts</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Polka dots</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></div>\n<h3>What does the warranty include?</h3>\n<p>When Joyride says this is “the last dog harness you’ll ever have to buy”, they mean it. If your harness is defective or breaks within 365 days of delivery, they’ll cover your purchase.</p>\n<h3>How do I measure my pet?</h3>\n<p>Joyride has a size guide on their website that you can reference to find the perfect fit for your pup. The sizing is <a href="https://www.dogster.com/dog-health-care/how-heavy-should-my-dog-be" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="internal">based on your dog’s weight and girth</a> (the widest part of their rib cage).</p>\n<h3>Is Pug Life Harness part of Joyride Harness?</h3>\n<p>Pug Life Harness and Joyride Harness are the same company. Joyride changed their name from Pug Life Harness to Joyride Harness a few years ago.</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-764044" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-name-tags.jpg" alt="Joyride Summer Mesh Harness Review - name tags" width="1500" height="1125" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-name-tags.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-name-tags-600x450.jpg.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-name-tags-800x600.jpg.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-name-tags-768x576.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-name-tags-250x188.jpg.webp 250w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Joyride-Summer-Mesh-Harness-Review-name-tags-500x375.jpg.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="http://shrsl.com/4vfwu" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Check Latest Price</span></a></div>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" widt