 class="su-button-center"><a href="https://www.instapainting.com/products/custphotoreal" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Check Price on Instapainting</span></a></div>\n<h3>Variety of Painting Mediums</h3>\n<p>You can select from the following mediums for your custom painting:</p>\n<div class="su-list" style="margin-left:0px">\n<ul>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Oil</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Watercolor</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Colored pencil</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Charcoal</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Pencil</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB"></i> Digital</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h3>Pick Your Own Artist</h3>\n<p>Instapainting has an extensive network of artists, all of whom submit bids for your painting proposal after placing your order! These artists apply to be on Instapainting, which already shows a deep love and investment for creating custom pieces for the company’s customers. The artists come from around the world, many based in Dafen Village. Dafen is renowned for its community of artists specializing in oil paintings.</p>\n<p>Because the artists submit after they’ve seen your reference material, you can feel confident that they are interested in what it is that you want. You will see a list of artists offering their portfolios to you, and then you can select the artist whose style you like the most.</p>\n<h3>Fully Customizable Painting Requests</h3>\n<p>Almost every aspect of your painting is fully customizable, from the size to the number of subjects. You can even adjust the methodology used to create your painting (whether you want something exactly like your reference or a bit more creative freedom). You can also leave notes for the artist on what you’d like added or changed, and keep in full communication.</p>\n<p>That being said, as this is a painting, there are limitations, and the artist will inform you of them.</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>About Instapainting</h2>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-764031" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Instapainting-Custom-Oil-Painting-Review-painting-on-a-shelf.jpg" alt="Instapainting Custom Oil Painting Review - painting on a shelf" width="1500" height="1126" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Instapainting-Custom-Oil-Painting-Review-painting-on-a-shelf.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Instapainting-Custom-Oil-Painting-Review-painting-on-a-shelf-600x450.jpg.webp 6