-Dog-Bakery-Lick-500x500.png.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>\n<p>Gift your dog a fancy treat this Easter with these <a href="https://www.dogster.com/redirects/?url=https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l8LeP/pubref:dogsteremaileasterbasket/destination:https://www.chewy.com/three-dog-bakery-lick-n-crunch/dp/203358" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">sandwich cookies by Three Dog Bakery</a>. These delicious cookies look just like ones you’d eat and have a real vanilla filling that’s sure to please your pup’s taste buds. They’re a bit high in calories for a dog treat, but Easter is a special occasion, and as long as you hand them out sparingly, it should be fine. And if you don’t think your pet will like vanilla, there are two other flavors they can try!</p>\n<hr />\n<h3>10. Claudia’s Canine Bakery Pink Passion Dog Cookie Assortment</h3>\n<div class="su-list" style="margin-left:0px">\n<ul>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB "></i> <strong>Our Choice: </strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00JW3L1TU/?tag=dogster-email-easter-basket-20&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">Claudia&#8217;s Canine Bakery Pink Passion Assortment of Gourmet Dog Cookies</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-749127" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Claudias-Canine-Bakery-Pink-Passion-Dog.png" alt="Claudia’s Canine Bakery Pink Passion Dog" width="500" height="500" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Claudias-Canine-Bakery-Pink-Passion-Dog.png.webp 1000w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Claudias-Canine-Bakery-Pink-Passion-Dog-600x600.png.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Claudias-Canine-Bakery-Pink-Passion-Dog-800x800.png.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Claudias-Canine-Bakery-Pink-Passion-Dog-768x768.png.webp 768w, http