p-content/uploads/2023/03/The-Lazy-Dog-Cookie-Co-800x800.png.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/The-Lazy-Dog-Cookie-Co-768x768.png.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/The-Lazy-Dog-Cookie-Co-400x400.png.webp 400w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/The-Lazy-Dog-Cookie-Co-250x250.png.webp 250w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/The-Lazy-Dog-Cookie-Co-500x500.png.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>\n<p>These <a href="https://www.dogster.com/redirects/?url=https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l8LeP/pubref:dogsteremaileasterbasket/destination:https://www.chewy.com/lazy-dog-cookie-co-mutt-mallows/dp/180909" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank">Mutt Mallows treats by The Lazy Dog Cookie Co.</a> sound fantastic, too. These cookies are vanilla-flavored and made with natural ingredients. They don’t contain wheat, soy, corn, and more, so they’re perfect for those with food sensitivities. They’re 24 calories a treat, but because they’re a soft cookie, you can break them into pieces for fewer calories at a time. This was another cookie that was a favorite of canines, so your dog will probably enjoy finding it in their Easter basket!</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716646" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 2 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>The 4 Easter Attires</h2>\n<p>Finally, what’s Easter without some dress-up fun? If your furball enjoys holiday attire, we have just the items to put in their Easter basket!</p>\n<h3>12. Frisco Hipster Hopster Dog &amp; Cat T-Shirt</h3>\n<div class="su-list" style="margin-left:0px">\n<ul>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB "></i> <strong>Our Choice: </strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Peeps-Comfortable-Washable-Officially-Licensed/dp/B08T17DZJ9/?tag=dogster-email-easter-basket-20&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">Peeps for Pets Call My Dog T Shirt</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-749129" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Hipster-Hopster-Dog.png" alt="Frisco Hipster Hopster Dog" width="500" height="500" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Hipster-Hopster-Dog.png.webp 1000w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Hipster-Hopster-Dog-600x600.png.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Hipster-Hopster-Dog-800x800.png.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Hipster-Hopster-Dog-768x768.png.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Hipster-Hopster-Dog-400x400.png.webp 400w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Hipster-Hopster-Dog-250x250.png.webp 250w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Hipster-Hopster-Dog-500x500.png.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>\n<p>Can it really be Easter if your pup isn’t wearing an Easter-themed shirt? As if the Peeps for Pets toys weren’t cute enough, there’s also an officially licensed <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Peeps-Comfortable-Washable-Officially-Licensed/dp/B08T17DZJ9/?tag=dogster-email-easter-basket-20&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">Peeps shirt</a>! This one has a witty saying (“Have your Peeps call my Peeps”) and is uber adorable. It doesn’t get much cuter than this, and wearing this shirt is pretty much guaranteed to make your dog the hit of Easter day.</p>\n<hr />\n<h3>13. Frisco Apple Dog &amp; Cat Bandana</h3>\n<div class="su-list" style="margin-left:0px">\n<ul>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB "></i> <strong>Our Choice: </strong><a href="https://www.dogster.com/redirects/?url=https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l8LeP/pubref:dogsteremaileasterbasket/destination:https://www.chewy.com/frisco-apple-dog-cat-bandana/dp/380015" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">Frisco Apple Dog &amp; Cat Bandana</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-749130" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Apple-Dog-Cat-Bandana.png" alt="Frisco Apple Dog &amp; Cat Bandana" width="500" height="500" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Apple-Dog-Cat-Bandana.png.webp 1000w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Apple-Dog-Cat-Bandana-600x600.png.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Apple-Dog-Cat-Bandana-800x800.png.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Apple-Dog-Cat-Bandana-768x768.png.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Apple-Dog-Cat-Bandana-400x400.png.webp 400w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Apple-Dog-Cat-Bandana-250x250.png.webp 250w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Frisco-Apple-Dog-Cat-Bandana-500x500.png.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>\n<p>Of course, some dogs won’t wear shirts, no matter how much you bribe them. For those canines, why not add a sweet fruity bandana to their basket? <a href="https://www.dogster.com/redirects/?url=https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l8LeP/pubref:dogsteremaileasterbasket/destination:https://www.chewy.com/frisco-apple-dog-cat-bandana/dp/380015" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank">This apple bandana by Frisco</a> is lovely and will absolutely jazz up your dog’s Easter vibes. Plus, it lends a <a href="https://www.dogster.com/lifestyle/diy-easter-egg-dogs" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="internal">hint of spring to any Easter celebration</a>. And if you’d rather have a bandana with bunnies or chicks, you should be able to find one easily enough!</p>\n<hr />\n<h3>14. Babole Pet Dog Collar Easter Gift with Bow Tie</h3>\n<div class="su-list" style="margin-left:0px">\n<ul>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB "></i> <strong>Our Choice:</strong> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09SWGFLBG/?tag=dogster-email-easter-basket-20&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">Dog Collar Easter Gift with Bow Tie</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-749131" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Babole-Pet-Dog-Collar-Easter-Gift.png" alt="Babole Pet Dog Collar Easter Gift" width="500" height="465" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Babole-Pet-Dog-Collar-Easter-Gift.png.webp 1000w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Babole-Pet-Dog-Collar-Easter-Gift-600x558.png.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Babole-Pet-Dog-Collar-Easter-Gift-800x744.png.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Babole-Pet-Dog-Collar-Easter-Gift-768x714.png.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Babole-Pet-Dog-Collar-Easter-Gift-250x233.png.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>\n<p>Bow ties are cool! So, why not toss one into your dog’s Easter basket? <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09SWGFLBG/?tag=dogster-email-easter-basket-20&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">This cute bow tie</a> is covered with Easter eggs and comes with an Easter collar to attach it to. The collar and bow tie are cotton, so they’ll be soft and gentle against your pet’s skin, and the collar has a snazzy metal buckle in case your dog wants to wear only that. The whole get-up is truly adorable, and your dog will look fabulous.</p>\n<hr />\n<h3>15. Bunny Ears</h3>\n<div class="su-list" style="margin-left:0px">\n<ul>\n<li><i class="sui sui-paw" style="color:#2575BB "></i> <strong>Our Choice:</strong> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B083HCQ7NF/?tag=dogster-email-easter-basket-20&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">Dog Bunny Ears and Easter Puppy Toy Kit</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-749132" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bunny-Ears.png" alt="Bunny Ears" width="500" height="500" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bunny-Ears.png.webp 1000w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bunny-Ears-600x600.png.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bunny-Ears-800x800.png.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bunny-Ears-768x768.png.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bunny-Ears-400x400.png.webp 400w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bunny-Ears-250x250.png.webp 250w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Bunny-Ears-500x500.png.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>\n<p>If nothing else, your dog should absolutely have bunny ears the next time Easter rolls around. These <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B083HCQ7NF/?tag=dogster-email-easter-basket-20&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">adorable bunny ears</a> also come with a carrot toy, so it’s a win-win! You get to see your pup looking extremely cute, and they get a fun rope toy after they’ve <a href="https://www.dogster.com/lifestyle/dog-behavior-dogs-wearing-clothes-naked" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="internal">suffered through the indignity of wearing bunny ears</a>. These ears are adjustable, so they can fit heads between four and eight inches; be sure to measure your pet’s head before purchasing!</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716646" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 2 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-05-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n<p>Everyone (and every pup) deserves to have an Easter basket! Creating a creative dog easter basket isn’t difficult, not once you have an idea of <a href="https://www.dogster.com/lifestyle/easte