le="width:0;background-color:#2575BB;color:#ffffff"><span><strong>Compatibility:</strong> 4.9/5</span></span></div>\n<p class="p1"><div class="sue-progress-bar sue-progress-bar-style-fancy sue-progress-bar-animation" style="background-color:#f0f0f0;border-color:#d6d6d6" data-percent="100"><span style="width:0;background-color:#2575BB;color:#ffffff"><span><strong>Directory:</strong> 5/5</span></span></div>\n<p class="p1"><div class="sue-progress-bar sue-progress-bar-style-fancy sue-progress-bar-animation" style="background-color:#f0f0f0;border-color:#d6d6d6" data-percent="100"><span style="width:0;background-color:#2575BB;color:#ffffff"><span><strong>Filtering:</strong> 5/5</span></span></div>\n<p class="p1"><div class="sue-progress-bar sue-progress-bar-style-fancy sue-progress-bar-animation" style="background-color:#f0f0f0;border-color:#d6d6d6" data-percent="98"><span style="width:0;background-color:#2575BB;color:#ffffff"><span><strong>Social Features:</strong> 4.9/5</span></span></div>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="https://www.dogpackapp.com/" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Visit Their Website</span></a></div>\n<p>As someone who wants her dog involved in every part of my life, we frequently travel together. She flies with me, goes on roadtrips, and participates in all my adventures. As anyone who travels frequently with their dog will tell you, finding pet-friendly services in a place you’ve never been can be stressful.</p>\n<p>So, what if I told you that there is an app out there, with a directory of thousands of dog-specific locations, that can be filtered by the amenities you want? What if I told you that you can search for a slew of pet services wherever you travel? That’s the beauty of the <a href="https://www.dogpackapp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="external">DogPack App</a>, an iOS and Android app that aims to be the one-stop shop for all dog-parenting needs. From a social network to an assistant providing daily care advice, this app is so much more than just a location finder.</p>\n<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>Overview</h2>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-765109" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-website-home-page.jpg" alt="DogPack App Review - website home page" width="1500" height="741" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-website-home-page.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-website-home-page-600x296.jpg.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-website-home-page-800x395.jpg.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-website-home-page-768x379.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-website-home-page-250x124.jpg.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="https://www.dogpackapp.com/" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Visit Their Website</span></a></div>\n<div class="su-table breed-table su-table-alternate">\n<table width="623">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width="90"><strong>Product Type:</strong></td>\n<td width="290">Website, iOS App, Android App</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="90"><strong>Best Suited For:</strong></td>\n<td width="290">Anyone with a dog</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="90"><strong>Price Range:</strong></td>\n<td width="290">Free</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="90"><strong>Countries Serviced:</strong></td>\n<td width="290">34 countries, including the USA</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="90"><strong>Types of Locations:</strong></td>\n<td width="290">Dog parks and dog beaches</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="90"><strong>Filtering:</strong></td>\n<td width="290">25 different amenity filters</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="90"><strong>Pet Businesses:</strong></td>\n<td width="290">52 different categories, including lodging</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width="90"><strong>Social Features:</strong></td>\n<td width="290">Social media-type feed</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>Our Experience</h2>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-765110" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-dog-on-a-trip.jpg" alt="DogPack App Review - dog on a trip" width="1500" height="1125" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-dog-on-a-trip.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-dog-on-a-trip-600x450.jpg.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-dog-on-a-trip-800x600.jpg.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-dog-on-a-trip-768x576.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-dog-on-a-trip-250x188.jpg.webp 250w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-dog-on-a-trip-500x375.jpg.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="https://www.dogpackapp.com/" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Visit Their Website</span></a></div>\n<p>I travel a lot with my dog, from local road trips to cross-country adventures. Even when we are home, I am always seeking new adventures for my 9-year-old mixed-breed Lorelei. However, wherever we end up, it can be a headache to find pet-friendly spots to walk around or pet services should she need a groom when we’re out of state. I knew I had to check it out when DogPack came across my feed (no pun intended).</p>\n<p>Although I have used dog-friendly locator websites in the past, I never knew there could be a phone app for one! The fact that DogPack is a handy app attracted me to the service. I quickly downloaded DogPack to my Android phone and got started right away.</p>\n<p>Upon opening the app, I was prompted to create an account. No personal information was asked for, just my email, a username, and a password. DogPack then requested that I make a profile for my dog, although you can always do that later! I filled in Lorelei’s information.</p>\n<p>The app opened first to the Feed, allowing me to start interacting with other pet owners immediately! I enjoyed seeing so many cute snouts and faces; everyone’s dogs looked like they were having an absolute blast. The feed gives the same feeling as Instagram and had many of the same features (Liking, Commenting, etc.). I posted a few images of my dog and got some likes and interactions fairly quickly!</p>\n<p>When it came time to explore the Map, I enabled Location Permissions on my phone and had it search my current area. I was in Beverly Hills then, and was enthused to see so many markers populate the map. Each marker was a different color, indicating a Dog Park, Dog-Friendly Location, Service, Lodging, etc. I could toggle which markers I wanted to see on my map through a bar at the top of the screen.</p>\n<p>Some of the marker selections on the map were a bit glitchy &#8211; a couple of markers required multiple taps of my finger for it to open. But alas, it is a phone app, glitches happen! This did not impede my enjoyment of DogPack.</p>\n<p>I decided that I wanted to locate a dog park specifically, and was happy to see that you can filter parks by amenities as well. I opened up Magic Johnson Dog Park and got to view the park’s star rating, list of amenities, description, weather (this is a super nice touch), dog count, and more.</p>\n<p>DogPack can also be accessed on a web browser, and although it limits some of the features, it was just as convenient to use as the app. The web version did make it a bit easier to read the blogs, I will say.</p>\n<p>I found that DogPack had a much more extensive collection of pet-friendly businesses, dog parks, and outdoor locations than the other websites I have used in the past. The other present features, such as the breed guides, made for fun late-night reading if I couldn’t sleep.</p>\n<p>The in-app currency, Treats, was a cute little touch &#8211; I liked that you could get discounts on the product store for DogPack just by using the app. There is a lot of incentivization for interacting with DogPack, and I honestly cannot believe this app is free. It is such a great resource!</p>\n<h2>Pros &amp; Cons</h2>\n<div class="su-row"><div class="su-column su-column-size-1-2"><div class="su-column-inner su-u-clearfix su-u-trim"><div class="su-box su-box-style-default" id="" style="border-color:#006600;border-radius:0px"><div class="su-box-title" style="background-color:#009906;color:#FFFFFF;border-top-left-radius:0px;border-top-right-radius:0px">Pros</div><div class="su-box-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim" style="border-bottom-left-radius:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px"><div class="su-list" style="margin-left:0px">\n<ul>\n<li><i class="sui sui-check" style="color:#00bf08"></i> Completely free</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-check" style="color:#00bf08"></i> Directory of pet services</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-check" style="color:#00bf08"></i> Worldwide</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-check" style="color:#00bf08"></i> Page for lost and found pets</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-check" style="color:#00bf08"></i> Integrated social media</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-check" style="color:#00bf08"></i> Great blog, breed guides, and more</li>\n<li><i class="sui sui-check" style="color:#00bf08"></i> Available for web, iOS, and Android</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class="su-column su-column-size-1-2"><div class="su-column-inner su-u-clearfix su-u-trim"><div class="su-box su-box-style-default" id="" style="border-color:#8c0000;border-radius:0px"><div class="su-box-title" style="background-color:#bf000a;color:#FFFFFF;border-top-left-radius:0px;border-top-right-radius:0px">Cons</div><div class="su-box-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim" style="border-bottom-left-radius:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px"><div class="su-list" style="margin-left:0px">\n<ul>\n<li><i class="sui sui-ban" style="color:#bf000a"></i> Like all apps, there are glitches</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>Key Features</h2>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-765113" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-features.jpg" alt="DogPack App Review - features" width="1500" height="741" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-features.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-features-600x296.jpg.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-features-800x395.jpg.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-features-768x379.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-features-250x124.jpg.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="https://www.dogpackapp.com/" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Visit Their Website</span></a></div>\n<h3>Dog Park Location Finder</h3>\n<p>The crowning jewel of DogPack is the extensive map of dog parks and dog-friendly outdoor locations! You can use the location services on your phone or type in an area to search for dog parks and/or pet-friendly spots.</p>\n<p>The map is fully interactive and customizable, with paw print indicators in different colors to signify what location is what. You can even filter dog parks based on their amenities to find the exact kind of spot that you want to take Fido to.</p>\n<p>Depending on how many people are active in an area, there is even a live tracker for how many people checked in for a specific park and how many dogs may be there.</p>\n<h3>Pet Services Directory and Listings</h3>\n<p>DogPack also shows dog services worldwide, from groomers, trainers, photographers, and so much more. This is especially helpful for those traveling with their dogs who may be in need of various services at their destination. You can filter services by type or view all available in a specific area via the map. You can even find pet-friendly hotels and lodging included in the directory.</p>\n<p>For pet businesses, listing is completely free! You do need to have an account, however. This is a great additional advertising for your pet-based service.</p>\n<h3>Social Media Feed</h3>\n<p>There is a very social aspect of DogPack, which can make it easy to schedule pup-dates and park meet-ups. The app has an actual feed page that looks similar to Instagram and Facebook. People post photos of their pups with captions, and you can Like, Comment, or post your own. DogPack allows you to Follow people, and they can become your Follower in return.</p>\n<p>This is an excellent way to connect with other pet owners in your area and organize doggy meetups, playdates, pack walks, and so much more.</p>\n<h3>Lost &amp; Found Pets, Breed Listings, and More</h3>\n<p>As if the above wasn’t enough, DogPack is slowly becoming the go-to dog resource with additional features.</p>\n<p>There is a dedicated page to post lost dogs (anyone pinging in the same area will receive an alert to keep an eye out for their missing pup) and found dogs.</p>\n<p>DogPack has a pervasive Breed Guide page, with some rare and unique breeds listed. As a <a href="https://www.dogster.com/dog-breeds/common-guide-dog-breeds" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="internal">dog breed enthusiast</a>, I can attest that the information I read on some uncommon breeds was sound and correct.</p>\n<p>The blog has a multitude of valuable and fun articles that help with all aspects of dog ownership. There is even a page dedicated to pet insurance!</p>\n<p>Earning Treats</p>\n<p>DogPack has an interesting rewards-based feature called Treats. Treats can be collected by referring friends to the app, completing specific tasks, or engaging and participating with DogPack. Treats can then be redeemed for rewards such as discounts on the DogPack store, raffle tickets, and even having your pup shared on the DogPack social media accounts.</p>\n<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>About DogPack</h2>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-765112" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-welcome-to-the-app.jpg" alt="DogPack App Review - welcome to the app" width="1500" height="1