>\n</div>\n<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>Is the DogPack App a Good Value?</h2>\n<p>The DogPak App is free &#8211; yes, you read that right, free! That makes it the best value of all, right? Moreover, the app itself is a tremendous value for its directory of locations and services alone.</p>\n<p>For all of us who want our pets included in every aspect of our lives, having a service to peek through pet-friendly amenities quickly is a significant enhancement to<a href="https://www.dogster.com/lifestyle/fun-things-to-do-with-your-dog" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-wpel-link="internal"> daily dog ownership life</a>. Adding a lost and found page, a dog breeds page, and a helpful blog makes the DogPack App invaluable.</p>\n<h3>How We Tested</h3>\n<p>The beauty of an app is that all I needed was my phone &#8211; I could test the service from the comfort of my couch! I have an Android phone, so I scanned the QR code from the DogPack website and launched the Google Play Store. After downloading the app, I created an account and got to searching. I proceeded to visit a couple of the local locations and verified that the information on those parks is indeed very accurate!</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-765111" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-app-filter.jpg" alt="DogPack App Review - app filter" width="1500" height="1093" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-app-filter.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-app-filter-600x437.jpg.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-app-filter-800x583.jpg.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-app-filter-768x560.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-app-filter-250x182.jpg.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="https://www.dogpackapp.com/" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Visit Their Website</span></a></div>\n<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="divider dog paws 3 oct 2024" width="2560" height="308" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-600x72.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-800x96.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-768x92.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-1536x185.webp 1536w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-2048x246.webp 2048w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-250x30.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>\n<h3>Do You Have To Have An Account To Use DogPack?</h3>\n<p>You do not need an account to browse the parks and business directory, but you need an account to use the other services offered by DogPack App. Creating an account is free!</p>\n<h3>What Is The Difference Between a Dog-Friendly Area and a Dog Park?</h3>\n<p>On the DogPack App, a dog-friendly area is a space not specifically designated for dogs, but dogs are welcome to visit. Marked red on the map, these locations typically require dogs to remain on-leash and don’t tend to have dog-specific amenities or facilities.</p>\n<p>An official dog park is marked green on the map and considered an actual dog park designated area (whether by the city or a private business). These locations allow off-leash use, can be fenced in, and have dog-specific features.</p>\n<h3>A Dog Park I Know Of Isn’t On The App &#8211; How Can I Submit One?</h3>\n<p>With an account on DogPack, you can suggest parks that may not be on the database already. To do so, navigate to the Dog Park page, which opens up a map. You can access this page by searching for an area using the search bar, clicking the “Explore” button, and selecting “Parks” from the dropdown menu.</p>\n<p>Once the map loads, click the Suggest a Pin button. Once the pin is in the proper place on the map, you can fill out information about the dog park, and then press Suggest Pin to close the window. The park will be reviewed by a DogPack admin once approved, you will receive a notification, and the park will be on the map.</p>\n<h3>An Amenity Listed For a Park Isn’t There &#8211; What Now?</h3>\n<p>DogPack offers a way to verify whether or not specific listed amenities are correct. You can vote on park amenities by navigating to the Amenities section on the park page and clicking <em>Vote on the Available Amenities</em>. You can always change your vote if an amenity that was there before is now gone.</p>\n<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-765114" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-amenities.jpg" alt="DogPack App Review - amenities" width="1500" height="1190" srcset="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-amenities.jpg.webp 1500w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-amenities-600x476.jpg.webp 600w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-amenities-800x635.jpg.webp 800w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-amenities-768x609.jpg.webp 768w, https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DogPack-App-Review-amenities-250x198.jpg.webp 250w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>\n<div class="su-button-center"><a href="https://www.dogpackapp.com/" class="su-button su-button-style-default" style="color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF6600;border-color:#cc5200;border-radius:12px" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px 30px;font-size:22px;line-height:44px;border-color:#ff944d;border-radius:12px;text-shadow:none"> Visit Their Website</span></a></div>\n<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-716648" src="https://www.dogster.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Dogster_Website-dividers_v1_Oct-1-2024-04-scaled.webp" alt="div